Current status
===================================
	
	* Initial public release together with bioRxiv publication.
	* Installable R package, not yet on bioconductor.
	* Includes a vignette for basic functionalities.
	* Function annotation not yet complete.
	* Usable for: 
		- Differential expression analysis (between groups of cells and across pseudotime)
		- Model fitting (e.g. continuous expression models as smooth model-based expression trajectories)
		- Plotting of continuous expression models
